reviewText: I had watched many episodes on television, but all were out of order.  Since I love the series. I decided trder the complete seasons.  Problem was one episode on each disc, something was wrong.  I contacted the seller and told him about it and he said return it and it would be replaced with another.  I did this, but had written what disc was defected with black ink. He returned it back again stating that they could not accept  the back because of the writing on the disc.  All he had to do was take a tissue and wipe my writing off.  Will not purchase from them again, and recommend that others do the same.

I just cannot get enough Criminal Minds.
